metadata.name: Yeva
metadata.description:
The 5000 Eva banknote was issued in Tokyo-3 by the Angel Bank in 2032. 
On the right side is Ayanami Rei - the zero pilot of giant robots. 
In the center is a stamp with a robot numbered 00.
Currency code: TKO32015HXD. 
By 2040, the banknote was issued in a circulation of 1,012,211 pieces.
